                <MadCap:snippetText src="../../Shared/Co-Fl-Li/Topics/Open-Content-File.flsnp" />
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>In the XML Editor, right-click on the marker holding the concept that you want to modify. From the context menu, select <span class="Emphasis">Edit the Concept Association</span>.</p>
                <MadCap:snippetBlock src="../../Shared/Co-Fl/Concepts/Concept-Window-Pane-Opens.flsnp" />
            </li>
            <li>In the <span class="Emphasis">Terms</span> column of the Concept window pane, click in the cell containing the keyword that you want to change.</li>
            <li>Type the concept and press <span class="Emphasis">ENTER</span>. The concept is modified.</li>
            <li>
                <MadCap:snippetText src="../../Shared/All/General/Save-File.flsnp" />
            </li>
